ADServe vendors a snapshot of jshttp/mime-db to code-generate its MIME-type table.

  Source:  https://github.com/jshttp/mime-db  (file: db.json)
  Version: 1.54.0
  Commit:  c03ddfcab556
  License: MIT

mime-db is the aggregate of the IANA media-type registry, Apache, and nginx. The vendored db.json
drives `ADServeMimeCodegen`, which emits the committed, reviewable
`Sources/ADServeCore/Generated/MIMEDatabase.swift`. To re-vendor: replace db.json with a newer
snapshot, update the version/commit above, and run `swift run ADServeMimeCodegen` (then `swift format`).

